## 15. Legal and Regulatory Compliance

15.1 **General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR)**
If you are located in the European Economic Area (EEA) or the United Kingdom, we process your personal data in compliance with the GDPR. You retain all rights provided under the GDPR, including the right to lodge a complaint with a supervisory authority.

15.2 **California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA)**
If you are a California resident, you may have additional rights under the CCPA, including the right to opt out of the sale of your personal information (although we do not sell personal information), and the right to non-discrimination for exercising your rights.

15.3 **Other Jurisdictions**
We also strive to comply with other applicable privacy and data protection laws. Please reach out to us if you have questions about our compliance in your jurisdiction.

